{"tid":2106180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有武肺確診者曾到西九龍捐血站捐血　","createTime":"2020-07-13T07:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T07:42:34.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8afe806c140ea624065d8bb51fd112c23634e76","tid":2106180,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:29:49.000Z","msg":"香港新冠肺炎疫情愈發失控，據悉今日(13日)至少有50宗確診個案。紅十字會輸血服務中心表示，接獲一名捐血者通知，他昨日（12日）確診新型肺炎，曾於本月5日下午到西九龍捐血站捐血，輸血服務中心現正跟進相關個案。<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會輸血服務中心指出，中心已自3月16日起，所有曾經離港人士，不論任何目的地，須在扺港當日起暫緩捐血28日。而曾與確診個案有密切接觸的人士，亦需暫緩捐血28日。中心又指所有捐血點皆遵行醫療服務處所的防疫措施，市民進入捐血站需佩帶口罩，並先量體溫及消毒雙手，站內設施亦加強消毒清潔，以確保捐血者及血液安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57da13b53c3597db7a50a1a70d653101425431f9","tid":2106180,"uid":2367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"依個時勢仲去捐血真係唔知話佢無私定蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c2134cf08c3ef1e6fbe691c0bf67eacc9493c3","tid":2106180,"uid":12154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">捐血家族</span>"},{"pid":"8f619f8fbc4d69ba5b456b35139e34c552f179a4","tid":2106180,"uid":220864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57da13b53c3597db7a50a1a70d653101425431f9","tid":2106180,"uid":2367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"依個時勢仲去捐血真係唔知話佢無私定蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:37:40.000Z","msg":"留意下紅十字同黑警捐血發生過咩事<br />\n可能個個就唔係單純蠢"},{"pid":"7836460e40c8ce32ba3aab08d8b693343fb021e7","tid":2106180,"uid":60835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:39:43.000Z","msg":"捐血師"},{"pid":"e62a607d3f018705fa8ed5077a5aa7f48b270c57","tid":2106180,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"7月5號仲去捐 一早話咗要杯角<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9Qhxop.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9Qhxop.png&h=6dd441cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bddcdebcbe54c7ffdea76efdf74cde78e90cc02","tid":2106180,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}